<plot>ART UNDER THE RADAR is a one-hour documentary that examines the other side of contemporary art, those artists who go against today's art establishment shock values and "uber" avant garde. Profiled are those who pursue painterly values and traditional techniques, artists who -- while they seldom make the headlines and rarely pull in astronomical auction prices -- have quite a bit to say about art and the art world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?046405</url></doc>
